3. 16,000,000 (Italy)
4. 9,000,000 (Poland)

10. 54,000 (Iceland)

Based on the map, Germany has the highest number of US Americans with ancestry at 45,000,000 people, followed by the United Kingdom/Great Britain with 34,000,000. These numbers reflect self-reported ancestry data, showing the significant European heritage of many Americans, particularly from Western and Northern European countries.
